  "summary": "看着像图论，实则因为是<strong>稠密图</strong>，不好直接跑，使用 dp 解决。",
  "link": "https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/1168/C",
  "link_text": "Problem - 1168C - Codeforces",
  "source": "",
  "aliases": [],
